<i>adverb</i>: 함부로 [함부로], 주책없이 [주채겁씨], 잘못 [잘몯], 무턱대고 [무턱때고], 무작정 [무작쩡], 무모히 [무모히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>함부로 [함부로]</dt><br>
<dd>thoughtlessly; carelessly; rashly; indiscreetly</dd><br>
<dd>조심하거나 깊이 생각하지 않고 마구.</dd><br>
<dd>Recklessly without being careful or thinking deeply.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>주책없이 [주채겁씨]</dt><br>
<dd>thoughtlessly</dd><br>
<dd>일정한 의견이나 주장이 없이 이랬다저랬다 하여 몹시 실없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that one is unreliable because he/she is fickle and does not have his/her own opinion or belief.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>잘못 [잘몯]</dt><br>
<dd>1. wrongly; incorrectly</dd><br>
<dd>바르지 않게 또는 틀리게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a way that is wrong or not right.</dd><br>
<dd>2. improperly; inappropriately</dd><br>
<dd>적당하지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a way that is not proper.</dd><br>
<dd>3. thoughtlessly; recklessly</dd><br>
<dd>깊이 생각하지 아니하고 함부로.</dd><br>
<dd>Carelessly without thinking deeply.</dd><br>
<dd>4. unfortunately; by bad luck</dd><br>
<dd>재수 없게.</dd><br>
<dd>Unluckily.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>무턱대고 [무턱때고]</dt><br>
<dd>blindly; thoughtlessly</dd><br>
<dd>잘 생각해 보지도 않거나 특별한 이유나 계획도 없이 마구.</dd><br>
<dd>At random without considering anything or without any special reason or plan.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>무작정 [무작쩡]</dt><br>
<dd>blindly; thoughtlessly</dd><br>
<dd>앞으로의 일에 대해 미리 생각하거나 정한 것이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without thinking about or considering something to come in the future.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>무모히 [무모히]</dt><br>
<dd>recklessly; thoughtlessly</dd><br>
<dd>일의 앞뒤를 생각하는 신중함이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without the carefulness with which one can think about the cause or effect of an incident.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>